com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.validation

Class URLActionDataExecutableResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xceptance.xlt.common.util.action.validation.URLActionDataExecutableResult

  • public class URLActionDataExecutableResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Offers a gentle way and various methods to access data of a WebRespone.
    Access Headers :
    • getHeaderByName(String)
    • getHeaders()
    • getCookie(), getCookieByName(String), getHttpCookies()
    Access Body :
    • getByRegEx(String)
    • getByXPath(String)
    Get response code: getHttpResponseCode()
    Get RAW response getWebResponse()
    Author:
    matthias mitterreiter
